  "title": "Infant Educator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Promotes feelings of security and trust in infants and toddlers</li>\n  <li>Responds positively to infants and toddlers’ needs, responses and cues</li>\n  <li>Provides routine care such as bathing, feeding, diapering, toileting, dressing and napping</li>\n  <li>Familiar with the steps and procedures in carrying out the routine care</li>\n  <li>Facilitates children’s exploratory behavior, thinking and learning</li>\n  <li>Plans and adapts activities to individual child’s needs</li>\n  <li>Supervises infants and toddlers at all times</li>\n  <li>Ensures that the environment is safe and healthy</li>\n  <li>Observes, reflects, evaluates and documents children’s learning, development and progress</li>\n  <li>Performs any other tasks assigned by the principal</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Higher Certificate in Infant Care or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Good verbal and written communication skills</li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and motivational skills</li>\n  <li>Ability to work independently and under pressure</li>\n  <li>Proactive and good team player<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
